'''Narharidas Barahath''' (नरहरिदास बारहठ) was a famous [[Rajasthani Language|Rajasthani]] poet of the medieval era. He was from the [[Charan]] family of the [[India]]n state [[Rajasthan]].
He was born in 1648 to Lakhaji in [[India]]n state [[Rajasthan]]. He was in the court of [[Jodhpur State]] king Gajsing I. He died there in about 1733.
